(221, 33, 'sectors_0_read_more_text', '<strong>Capital markets communications advice</strong>\r\n\r\nFocusing on financial PR and investor relations, Camarco provides specialist capital markets communications advice and has advised on numerous high profile M&amp;A events, IPOs, equity and debt issuances. The team members are all experts in dealing with restructurings, refinancings and regulatory and legal investigations. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Ed Gascoigne-Pees</a> leads this offer.\r\n\r\n<strong>Corporate and b2b communications</strong>\r\n\r\nCamarco can also ensure that the specific products offered by financial services companies (both institutional and retail) obtain the correct profile and reputation amongst the target media and audiences. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Louise Dolan</a> leads the firm’s offer on corporate and b2b communications.\r\n\r\n<strong>Regulatory advice</strong>\r\n\r\n<a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Lindsay Thomas</a> leads this service and advises clients on how to approach and communicate with the regulator in an ever more demanding and complex regulatory environment. We also provide training for clients who may need to prepare for Treasury Select Committees and are undergoing regulatory investigations.'),
