(253, 34, 'sectors_1_read_more_text', 'The strategy for the energy and resources team is to work with a select number of high quality clients covering the various sub sectors and geographies. Our experience within the sector allows us to advise clients on every aspect of their communications with the key stakeholders that matter to the senior management teams.\r\n\r\nWe advise companies on their relations with investors, sell-side analysts and the press to ensure these, often capital intensive companies, can access capital efficiently and when it is needed. The team has specific experience with resource IPOs, buy and sell-side M&amp;A, crisis management and defending energy companies from activist investors. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Billy Clegg</a> leads this offer.\r\n\r\nThe team is well placed to advise its clients on their relations with the Governments and communities who are impacted by their operations, ensuring clients have a long and sustainable license to operate.'),
