(291, 35, 'sectors_2_read_more_text', 'We advise companies on their relations with investors, sell-side analysts and the press to ensure our clients can access capital efficiently and when it is needed.\r\n\r\nThe team has specific experience with consumer IPOs, demergers, restructurings, buy and sell-side M&amp;A, crisis management and investor relations.<a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Geoffrey Pelham-Lane </a>leads this offer.'),
