(294, 35, '_sectors_3_title', 'field_568e8bb041624'),
(295, 35, 'sectors_3_text', 'Camarco has expertise across the industrials sector, which encompasses a broad range of sub sectors including infrastructure and construction, support services, utilities, aerospace and defence, manufacturing and engineering. These industries face a diverse range of challenges and often have to operate within highly competitive or highly regulated markets subject to the vagaries of government policy.'),
(296, 35, '_sectors_3_text', 'field_568e8be041625'),
(297, 35, 'sectors_3_add_read_more', 'Yes'),
(298, 35, '_sectors_3_add_read_more', 'field_568e8c1941626'),
(299, 35, 'sectors_3_read_more_text', 'The focus for the industrials team is to provide insightful and solid advice based on past experience. We often manage PR and IR in relation to business critical issues for clients. Over many years we have worked on every scenario such as plane crashes, asbestos, supply chain disruptions, product recalls, M&amp;A and bid defences – as well as helping companies to establish consistent stock market valuations which reflect the underlying strength of their brands, business models and prospects.\r\n\r\nOur strategy is to retain and grow our strong reputation within the industrials sectors, ensuring that our clients are always well understood by the key investment commentators from within the sell-side analysts, media and investors. Most importantly, we pride ourselves on the depth of sector knowledge we have as well as strong contacts and time-sensitive market intelligence.\r\n\r\nOver recent years there has been a period of consolidation across some of the industrials sub-sectors and we have been actively involved advising on high profile M&amp;A transactions – both on the defence and aggressor sides. The campaigns we have led include investor, media, analysts, customer and employee relations.\r\n\r\nWithin the regulated and utilities industries we have spearheaded campaigns to launch new local government initiatives as well as being cognisant of the wider regulatory environment.\r\n\r\n<a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Ginny Pulbrook</a> leads this offer.'),
