(303, 35, 'sectors_4_text', '<div class="content"><section class="page full"><article>Camarco has extensive experience across the real estate and housebuilding sectors, including high profile advisory roles for FTSE 250 companies, REITS as well as private companies.\r\n\r\n</article></section></div>'),
