(307, 35, 'sectors_4_read_more_text', 'Our IR expertise is invaluable in ensuring that the investment community and investment commentators understand our clients’ particular positions within the property sector, the income producing potential of the various asset classes they own and the ability to unlock the latent value of assets through management’s actions.\r\n\r\nThe diverse nature of the sector means that we know and understand complex businesses and are well placed to manage Company’s City relations for on-going financial communications, M&amp;A, special situations and crisis management. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Ginny Pulbrook</a> and <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Ed Gascoigne-Pees</a> lead this offer.'),
