(386, 37, '_sectors_0_title', 'field_568e8bb041624'),
(387, 37, 'sectors_0_text', 'Camarco has expertise across all the financial services sub-sectors. The partners have worked with the world’s largest international banks, insurance companies, pension firms, asset managers, wealth managers, exchanges, alternative finance providers, private equity firms and listed funds.'),
