(390, 37, '_sectors_0_add_read_more', 'field_568e8c1941626'),
(391, 37, 'sectors_0_read_more_text', '<strong>Capital markets communications advice</strong>\r\n\r\nFocusing on financial PR and investor relations, Camarco provides specialist capital markets communications advice and has advised on numerous high profile M&amp;A events, IPOs, equity and debt issuances. The team members are all experts in dealing with restructurings, refinancings and regulatory and legal investigations. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Ed Gascoigne-Pees</a> leads this offer.\r\n\r\n<strong>Corporate and b2b communications</strong>\r\n\r\nCamarco can also ensure that the specific products offered by financial services companies (both institutional and retail) obtain the correct profile and reputation amongst the target media and audiences. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Louise Dolan</a> leads the firm’s offer on corporate and b2b communications.\r\n\r\n<strong>Regulatory advice</strong>\r\n\r\n<a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Lindsay Thomas</a> leads this service and advises clients on how to approach and communicate with the regulator in an ever more demanding and complex regulatory environment. We also provide training for clients who may need to prepare for Treasury Select Committees and are undergoing regulatory investigations.'),
(392, 37, '_sectors_0_read_more_text', 'field_568e8c2f41627'),
(393, 37, 'sectors_1_title', 'Energy & Resources'),
(394, 37, '_sectors_1_title', 'field_568e8bb041624'),
(395, 37, 'sectors_1_text', 'Camarco has expertise across the energy and resources sector. The team has worked with some of the world’s finest independent oil, oil services, renewable energy, gold, coal, and iron ore companies.'),
(396, 37, '_sectors_1_text', 'field_568e8be041625'),
(397, 37, 'sectors_1_add_read_more', 'Yes'),
(398, 37, '_sectors_1_add_read_more', 'field_568e8c1941626'),
(399, 37, 'sectors_1_read_more_text', 'The strategy for the energy and resources team is to work with a select number of high quality clients covering the various sub sectors and geographies. Our experience within the sector allows us to advise clients on every aspect of their communications with the key stakeholders that matter to the senior management teams.\r\n\r\nWe advise companies on their relations with investors, sell-side analysts and the press to ensure these, often capital intensive companies, can access capital efficiently and when it is needed. The team has specific experience with resource IPOs, buy and sell-side M&amp;A, crisis management and defending energy companies from activist investors. <a title="Our People" href="http://www.camarco.co.uk/our-people/">Billy Clegg</a> leads this offer.\r\n\r\nThe team is well placed to advise its clients on their relations with the Governments and communities who are impacted by their operations, ensuring clients have a long and sustainable license to operate.'),
(400, 37, '_sectors_1_read_more_text', 'field_568e8c2f41627'),
(401, 37, 'sectors_2_title', 'Consumer Industries'),
(402, 37, '_sectors_2_title', 'field_568e8bb041624'),
(403, 37, 'sectors_2_text', 'Camarco has long standing expertise in a number of sub sectors within consumer industries, most notably travel and leisure, retail and motor retail.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
