(491, 57, 'profiles_0_biography', 'Ed has worked in the financial services sector for 17 years.  He has advised high profile global clients on all aspects of communications within the financial markets, including large scale M&amp;A, IPOs, restructuring, legal and regulatory investigations and governmental defaults.\r\n<div class="biography">\r\n\r\nClient experience includes Bain Capital, Zurich Insurance Group, Jupiter Asset Management, Dubai World, Northern Rock, Towergate and Polar Capital.\r\n\r\nEd was previously a Senior Managing Director within FTI Consulting’s Strategic Communications division, formerly known as Financial Dynamics which he joined in 2003. Before that he was in investment banking with Macquarie and Brown Shipley. Prior to investment banking, Ed worked in the audit &amp; advisory practice of Deloitte where he worked in the Financial Services team. Ed qualified as a chartered accountant from Deloitte.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:ed.gascoigne-pees@camarco.co.uk">ed.gascoigne-pees@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4984\r\n\r\n</div>'),
