(817, 61, 'profiles_10_biography', 'Jenny joined Camarco from GlobalCapital magazine where she was Supplements Editor.  She had been a financial journalist for more than eight years, specialising in retail asset management. She has had work published in popular finance titles such as What Investment, Growth Company Investor, Investment Adviser and FTAdviser.com, alongside national newspapers including FTfm, The Times and The Sunday Times.\r\n\r\nIn 2010, Jenny was awarded the coveted Financial Consumer Journalist of the Year by the Association of Investment Companies and in both 2012 and 2013 she was part of the editorial team that scooped the IMA Team Award for Excellence in Investment Writing.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:jenny.lowe@camarco.co.uk">jenny.lowe@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4990'),
