(883, 2, 'profiles_12_biography', 'Gordon has over 8 years of experience in the communications and capital market sectors, advising international clients on their financial and corporate communications.\r\nGordon has particular experience advising mining and resource companies on their financial calendar communications, developing integrated engagement programmes, investor relations, IPO, international M&amp;A and crises communications.\r\n\r\nGordon was previously a Director at Buchanan where he advised companies such as Centamin, Endeavour Mining, Sinarmas Group, Aureus Mining, Mineral IRL, Azonto Petroleum and Archipelago Resources. Prior to Buchanan Gordon was a practicing solicitor at Boodle Hatfield.\r\n\r\nMail: gordon.poole@camarco.co.uk\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4997'),
