(919, 62, 'profiles_2_biography', 'Billy has worked in strategic communications for over 15 years, having advised a wide range of international companies from the FTSE 100, FTSE 250, and on AIM.\r\n<div class="text">\r\n<div class="biography">\r\n\r\nBilly has particular experience advising energy and resource companies and retail and motor retail companies on financial calendar communications, investor relations, IPO, complicated M&amp;A and on shareholder activism situations.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Camarco, Billy spent nine years at FTI Consulting’s Strategic Communications division, formerly known as Financial Dynamics where he advised companies such as Ophir Energy, Inchcape, Transocean, Vertu Motors, Sherborne Investors, BAE Systems, Amerisur Resources and Cove Energy. Prior to Financial Dynamics, Billy spent six years at Bell Pottinger Financial. Billy also has experience as Head of Communications at Andes Energia. Billy is a Fellow of the Geological Society and a Director of the Scottish Oil Club.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:billy.clegg@camarco.co.uk">billy.clegg@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4983\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
