(927, 62, 'profiles_3_biography', '<p class="job_title">Louise has over 20 years’ of media and communications experience specialising in pensions, investments and wealth management. She started her career at National Mutual, a specialist pension firm before moving into agency life. She worked at Polhill, Lansons and was most recently a Managing Director in FTI Consulting’s Strategic Communications division, formerly known as Financial Dynamics which she joined in 2000.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="biography">\r\n\r\nLouise is a media relations and communications specialist and has developed a network of top tier business and financial contacts. In addition to successfully running critically acclaimed campaigns and on-going public relations programmes, Louise is highly experienced in issues and change management having headed a number of sensitive projects for global organisations. Client experience includes AMPS, AXA Wealth, BlackRock, Courtiers, Coutts, Collins Stewart, Credit Suisse, Dentons, Goldman Sachs, ING, Mattioli Woods, Morgan Stanley, Platform Black, Polar Capital, Talbot &amp; Muir, Sanlam, Smith &amp; Williamson, and Suffolk Life.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:louise.dolan@camarco.co.uk">louise.dolan@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4982\r\n\r\n</div>'),
