(935, 62, 'profiles_4_biography', 'She has worked in financial corporate communications for over 20 years, having held senior media relations roles with RBS, BlackRock, Goldman Sachs and Citi.\r\n\r\nRebecca has extensive capital markets experience, developing and executing media strategies on a variety of products and technically specialist areas across the UK, Ireland and EMEA.  She has worked on the launches of Rothesay Life and Source, and promoted the inaugural benchmark bonds for the International Finance Facility for Immunisation (IFFIm).  Rebecca is skilled at developing messages around sensitive and contentious issues such as change and crisis management situations.'),
