(967, 62, 'profiles_8_biography', 'Jennifer has over nine years’ experience in the communications and financial markets sectors, advising clients on a broad range of critical communications issues with a particular focus on corporate and financial communications, M&amp;A and equity capital market transactions.\r\n\r\nJennifer has extensive experience in developing integrated engagement programmes for clients with key audiences and stakeholders, investor relations and financial calendar work, internal communications, media relations, profile building, corporate responsibility positioning and reputation management.  Jennifer has also advised on a number of high profile M&amp;A, IPO and equity capital market transactions in EMEA and Asia across a range of industries.\r\n\r\nClient experience includes BTG Pactual, Lombard Odier IM, ETF Securities, Barclays, Numis Securities, HMV, London Mining, Serco, ISS, and SKIL Ports and Logistics.\r\n\r\nJennifer previously worked at Brunswick Group and prior to that was an investment banker at Citi, working in their M&amp;A and Equity Capital Market teams in both London and Hong Kong.\r\n\r\nmail: <a href="mailto:jennifer.renwick@camarco.co.uk" target="_blank">jennifer.renwick@<wbr />camarco.co.uk\r\n</a>Direct no: 020 3757 4990'),
