(1162, 63, '_profiles_6_job_title', 'field_568e88bfe1a69'),
(1163, 63, 'profiles_6_biography', '<p class="job_title">Georgia specialises in financial and corporate communications across a range of sectors.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="biography">\r\n\r\nMost recently, Georgia has advised companies such as Bonmarché, Hobbs, DFS, Sports Direct, Caracal Energy, Faroe Petroleum and Ithaca Energy.\r\n\r\nGeorgia has advised on a number of high profile M&amp;A, IPO and capital raising transactions; most recently Bonmarché on its listing in November 2013, Cove Energy on its $1.9bn sale to PTT, Ithaca Energy’s acquisition of Valiant Petroleum, and on the London IPOs of Ophir Energy and Caracal Energy.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Camarco, Georgia was a Director at FTI Consulting. Before this she worked in New York in a marketing role and studied for the Certificate in International Business Practice. Georgia graduated from Exeter University in 2007 with a BA (Hons) in History.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:georgia.mann@camarco.co.uk">georgia.mann@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4986\r\n\r\n</div>'),
