(1171, 63, 'profiles_7_biography', 'Hazel has worked in financial communications and journalism for over 8 years. She specialises in M&amp;A, debt communications and financial restructurings, including non-financial stakeholder communications around such events.\r\n\r\nClient experience includes Bain Capital, Deutsche Bank, Dubai World, Heineken, Croda, Rusal, INEOS and Endemol.\r\n\r\nHazel was previously a Director within FTI Consulting’s Strategic Communications division, formerly known as Financial Dynamics which she joined in 2007. Before that she was a journalist with Debtwire where she covered debt restructurings and high yield and leveraged loans and before that covered Eurobonds and structured finance at Informa Global Markets. She is a graduate in Natural Sciences from the University of Cambridge.\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href="mailto:hazel.stevenson@camarco.co.uk">hazel.stevenson@camarco.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\nDirect no: 020 3757 4989'),
